re very vulnerable when driving i think we re most human in moments like that so it hard not to recognize others existences i m really feeling the human connection recently i was brought to tears not synonymous with wanting to be away from you so many friendships shattered over this misunderstanding i m haunted by daydreams of what my fullest potential could be had i been born in a world free of money and agendas i was not born to be a slave in corporate society and that why i often struggle with happiness thx for your love keep spreading it ppl like u are the reason the world hasn t gone up in flames forever in love w my infp poll what do you need to work on when it comes to romantic relationships i am the sun and i am the moon i trust myself but i think i m crazy i know nothing but i also know everything me as well suppression of affection has always been one of my struggles i m such a loving person but not many would ever know why cant i small talk why do i only breed words on obscure topics why cant i talk abt the weather w out bringing up global warming i m really bad at being affectionate which makes no sense considering the swarm of butterflies in my stomach at all times hi lovely lady thank u so much i often go thru periods of time where i m at a loss for words amp don t feel confident in my wit i don t care how beautiful or intelligent or sweet you are if my initial instincts say no then you ve got to go poll what would your perfect autumn day consist of once i m in a routine everything is easy but if one thing throws me off schedule then i spend the next month trying to catch up you are a breath of fresh air within humanity pollution even the butterflies know it i m the most optimistic pessimist i know poll how would you best identify yourself when it comes to the idea of a god source supreme being it really frustrating how my personality is dependent on how comfortable i am my greatest talent making up excuses those am i actually anor just bipolar moments i swear i m a cool outgoing person just give me like more hangout sessions to prove it summer is the time when introverts are forced into uncomfortable situations just because it in season halfway done w and it been nothing but a challenge i suggest meditation and less social media for those who are empathic like me so handsome p dark circles are a sign of a hardworking or deep thinking individual i talk highly of the moon and poorly of society priorities i m a computer that goes into sleep mode when i m forced to be around people i don t vibe with note to self if i don t dislike you then i probably love you and vice versa because there no gray area when it comes to who i spend my time on why are u crying ur thinking way too much into things have u figured out your life plan yet aw u should smile more i made a blog about humanity and i hope it goes nowhere so i ll keep being honest when i grow tired of fantasizing about my future i switch gears and fantasize about my next existence i m a type which basically means i m the personification of an everlasting sigh if there a way to have extremely low self esteem but somehow manage to be self absorbed i ve figured it out i m good at pretending to be a socialite when i have to be but that doesn t mean my insides aren t screaming runnnnnnn how did i end up with one of the most socially up in your face jobs on the planet how have i survived am i even alive when you re hanging out with someone and they go i invited a couple friends to come too if that cool i wish and wish and wish for something but when the opportunity is finally handed to me i feel like i m being suffocated telling me to stop overanalyzing will actually have the opposite effect because you re basically announcing one of my insecurities i love you so because you balance me out in the most natural of ways caution strangers i will read you and determine my feelings for you and predict your future all within our second encounter i fell in love and it tops my list of the most melodramatic things i ve done thus far a majority of my friendships relationships are long distance and i wonder if i meant for it to be this way from the beginning i enjoy the simple things in life but i ll never live a simple life masochism avoid tomorrow by staying up as late as possible resulting in less sleep amp making the day more unbearable than originally some days it near impossible for me to get words out no matter how active my brain is and let me tell you it one of those days doesn t communicate doesn t get what i want it not my fault you didn t pick up on my signals i made them very clear this time my tweets will eventually contradict each other as a reflection of my actual mind forever in a state of guilt for things happening on other continents to people i don t know waits so many days to return someone call that i have to fake a story about how i left my phone on the moon and just got it back oh please excuse the crystal ball in my brain idk how i ve survived this complex of being if i don t feel a magnetic pull towards you from the beginning don t get excited about the fate of our acquaintance the i actually stands for indecisive when someone mentions myers briggs at a social gathering learning to shed the outer layers that aren t needed and go back to the purest form of me my love for people cannot be contained in the realms of technology in other words sorry i didn t text back again if not careful falling in love means fading away i am erratic in the calmest way possible and the paradoxes don t stop there extroversion is the key to success but introversion is the key to my house which is way more comfortable how do i balance my love for humans and my hatred for society new years resolution find a diet to lose the weight of the world

what we resolved to do to absorb the energy of all those i know and love is completely and utterly exhausting my idea of cleaning is more of a gathering amp dumping of piles from many rooms into designated hidden areas i often fill others lives with positive affirmations while trying to quiet the internal chatter in my head of negative insecurities i ll politely smile when you show me the polished surface of your life amp soon i ll be asking about the dustiest corners of your reality enfps can t balance their checkbooks very well but they can balance the emotions of about close friends at the same time not i want people to connect with me but i also need time away love me love my space what a peaceful day it would be to blindfold myself from seeing all sides of every problem every feeling and every outcome if you re an enfp there a good chance someone has lied to you about the actual time something starts just to get you there on time it not that enfps are never running early it just that when we are we feel like we have time to do something on the way then we re late an enfp ability to sum up a situation correctly in a short amount of time is sometimes even shocking to them at work enfps can often be the go to for those seeking support amp empathy be wary of energy consumed from being an emotional dumping ground checks phone messages work related from friend saying do you have time to talk no question which one i respond to first enfps can feel overextended when their drive amp energy creates a leadership role but their preference is to be equal amp explore together enfps search for perfect gifts a gift card just seems too impersonal then we take forever deciding run out of time amp buy a gift card to reveal so much of my soul that others always see the real me my ultimate goal and my ultimate fear enfps try so hard to make the best holiday for everyone else it is our joy but should not be at the expense of our own enjoyment i can make a decision quickly if it involves various paths it easily changed amp i can go back if i don t like it enfps spend a lot of time living life and then recovering from life enfps are never just hearing the words you say we are connecting the subtleties behind the words amp searching for how you really feel journeys are much more interesting to me than conclusions laundry istj finds an unmatched sock searches for where it may be enfp adds single socks to previous pile in room finds a match enfp in public enfp alone we solve emotional crime scenes on the daily why did he make that face is she sad he seemed disappointed that moment when you say something amp no one responds so you keep explaining what you said but still there silence i hate that moment you either love us for our overly passionate empathic nature or hate us for our overly passionate empathic nature enfps are quite the perceptive personality we see through so many defense mechanisms amp passive aggressive ways that it difficult to trust amazing how a quiet morning recharges this extrovert i bounce off the energy of others so much it refreshing to be still enfps can disappear from your life when trying to juggle too many things at once we constantly shift our priorities so we ll be back soon enfps can benefit from a temporary flexible volunteer job helping others is usually the best thing for our self esteem i often give energy to something and crash with energy left things are rarely with me forever editing my wordiness of emotions when composing work emails me daily i once apologized for my messy house by blaming it on my p ness strangest looks ever an enfp can be so lost in a good conversation they will often jolt up in a panic saying wait what time is it i totally forgot to looking in the cushions of the couch for the remote you just lost and finding the cordless phone you lost months ago probs because i never make firm plans for the day my day can be quickly consumed by those who do this i wait to see how i feel about so many things before i make a decision that it overwhelms me and i basically never decide i will jump through hoops to help a friend but show me an online return policy with steps and i won t take the time to return something this was like free therapy i can tell you anything chances are if you are an enfp you ve heard this more than once i am exhausted after a social event because i m constantly assessing how things are going what i said how others are reacting etc i get irritated if i have too many things to do in a day yet i start amp not finish many projects at a time enfps don t excel at short conversations we will walk back to a conversation with one more thing i forgot to tell you over amp over again enfp in a group text friend hi friend hello friend hi me texting privately everything ok how are you really doing i have such a hard time turning people down that my no often sounds like a maybe it hard to have something you love about your personality reflected back as too sensitive or dramatic as an enfp i m so happy you like what i have to say i read negative meaning into words that are not extreme if you say fine ok or yeah i will assume something not quite right i have a silent project wave challenge going on w my neighbors it is my goal to get them to wave back don t just agree with me to agree with me i want you to passionately reflect on things i say amp challenge me to see things in a new way if we are talking with someone who has nothing in common with us enfps start to dig we will use humor or insight to find a common ground enfps do buy birthday cards we just put them aside until we can add a meaningful note then forget to send them intuitive people watching i m always finishing big projects myself because i don t want to put people out or don t plan far enough in advance to ask for help you are right when it comes to brainstorming about what could be i do that but am very bad at planning amp organizing ahead enfps are good at living in the moment we forget too much to live in the past amp we re often too unorganized to focus far into the future because we are able to read what people need enfps usually want the same in return telling people how to meet their needs feels unnatural

or ripe to hear direct experience or wisdom respect that move on today is that rd monday in january watch your actions amp your wordswith others today be a light unto someone dbad was a year filled with wishes accepting not settling everything just as it is and appreciating it all just so you are intelligent beautiful and worthy of anyone company attention amp appreciation don t let anyone tell you differently today so many people are expressing how bad was we re all connected and are affected by one another actions because we re all one and this too we shall all forget be proud of your own accomplishments rather than seeking approval from others self care comes first theworld will have to wait letgo be thankful each and every day about something anything it what keepsus going sometimes youjust have to stop the world from spinning so that you can get off allow peace to be still sometimes you have to be thatperson that stands up amp speaks out amidst turmoil to remind people we are today be he or she sometimes to feel better when youare feeling down the only way up is toreflect on gratitude and help someone else out knowing what to let go intelligence why to let go mindfulness when to let go growth letting go wisdom i mblessed manydays i don trealize it can tevenimaginehow so but the fact that i mbreathing in thismoment is proof what ever you do today do it with grace and withoutjudgment and just watch how the day unfolds withlimitless joy instead of being intimidated by the strength of another become inspiredinstead hate burns useful energy and benefits no one faith cannotexistwith our patience sometimes we justhave to wait andsee in a positive place right now livingin themoment moment by moment intending to watch clouds of emotions go by on this monday decide to choose love instead in your speech in your intentions in your livelihood inyour efforts actions in your livelihood one can not stand in the midst of falling sometimes you must hit rock bottom broke before you are able to stand firmly on feet meditation is a playground for thoughts not a prison giving a piece of yourself to help someone is not equal to giving away your peace it so important to recognize the difference for all who had a bad day may tomorrow bring down a rain fall of awesometastic blessings that will keep you uplifted throughout the day appreciate and express gratitude to and forall which has brought you to this very moment in time each moment we are all blessed with glimpses of enlightenment allow those moments to show you happiness instead of busy building paths when we begin to see things just as they really are we become awake and wise still easily clouded by judgment attachment greed amp hatred seeing things as they truly are is not enlightenment seeing things as they truly are and accepting without judgement is enlightenment interview with cbs news cbs挞 tracee carrasco reports sometimes in the darkest moments of your life you can see clearer than you ever have lifting maya enjoying the sound of silence at work before all idle chatter begins there will be those who don t know your struggle who don t understand your hustle stay true to yourself convert that energy into muscle when did emails and texts become as urgent as phone calls and visits just going to sit here and watch the sun come up sometimes in your life you have to coach yourself and be your own cheerleader and that okay just don t ever become a spectator sometimes the only way out of hell is to go straight through it it actually victorious once you awakento it today i will celebrate all kidney recipients because everyday is a new birthday happy birthday today mom birthday is today without a kidney transplant i would be mourning today instead we are celebrating full moon energy can be overwhelming at times change is inevitable right why not be more proactive amp make changes on your own stop waiting for happiness to just happpen credit cards amp scores taxes tv projects amp gated communities marriage corporate america ads amp logos tracking devices tuition freedom remember to pace yourselves today you re happiness should not depend on plans and dreams of anyone else but your own mindful not to fall back into old patterns puts some thingin perspective sometimes when the people closest to you areunavailable to you you have to depend on the kindness of strangers i love you too know your worth keep seeing this over and over again in the past week paying attention do and say what you believe is right even if it shakes you gives you butterflies or drys your throat take a break from everythingyou believe in conditioned thought let go of all attachments and see if and how you survive absolutely what is conceived in darkness will evolve into the light act in a way as if a spotlight is on you even if no one is watching when your patience meter is on tilt retreat meditate and reset repeat as needed nothing we re all one with so many people surrounding you east west north south how can one possibly focus on receiving love or attention from just person get up get out go live and perceive every detour today as a blessing keeping you from falling off your true path living this day to its fullest no schedule no plan no clock until the sun sets if your parent are still with us call them do something for them or something nice for someoneelse and dedicate the merits to them sometimes the most compassionate thing you can do for someone is to just pay attention to them those who are disturbed by you walking away from something may be experiencing their own room for doubt in the present moment you don t have to go away to retreat it can be done anywhere take time in in your life or in your day to stop and reflect or just be smile like it doesn t hurt converted to a rural landscape get away from people who equate egotism with bold decisive visionary leadership hey mickey r who will you scam for income when the trust fund runs out wants are not identical to needs mature people know the difference there enough finra action going on around here to shake a stick at if i had a stick i answer the phone when it rings i hang up if the caller is wasting my time i listen if i know who they are i ll need to be a billionaire if i want a cabinet appointment someday why say howdy in your intro your museum isn t in texas foreign tourists may become confused twitter claims my tweets are on fire okay i ll play along there will never be a chinese dim sum concept for fast food restaurant chains there would be too many combos for a drive thru menu the world was never simpler than today more primitive certainly but human nature was never simple through history preparing for war is more serious than making a sandwich a lot of people with m or more are not prepared for a debt currency crisis asset mix matters invest in yourself first even if the dividends are invisible unbelievable performance and probably unsustainable lolthis is why i won t go to coachella we ve all heard of big pharma biohacking and d printing will usher in small pharma definitely skill badges and tabs most people find superficial first impressions to be meaningful sad but true it is good to enjoy potato chips while pursuing one bonanza imitation crabmeat doesn t fool me i can tell it pretending even behind the funny disguise they expect pls to have prior enlisted time the one thing that confers instant credibility upon an officer whatever happened to the killer bee invasion back in the maybe they all got lost on their way to the us border those others are often pre occupied with flattery self confident people then hear how much they should love themselves we saw this in the dot com era with kozmo and others it always ends the same way variable costs are stern masters screenshot a gets my attention the pale blue sky in the background is a starker contrast with the text block shading i suspect that pancake mix is really just a fancy name for flour a brokerage that gave away a free garden hose for opening an account would get my attention but not my money banks no longer give away free toasters when you open an account those were the good old days gold just sits and stares stare back all you like it does not respond it definitely the journal i was looking for calm down san francisco plenty of places in the us have seen worse storms i have always likedand planters snacks especially dry roasted peanuts auditors coming have donuts out works like a charm every time you re welcome in advance the bacon explosion is still around somewhere someone should make a vegan equivalent it is good to leave a legacy of bonanza yesyou are brexit and us electoral surprise prove that economic growth skewed toward elites brings instability know exactly what the internet needs more cat videos do not listen to julian assange he is anti american and should stand trial to answer criminal charges china obor is about more than development it enables power projection strategic encirclement and ultimately militarism think twice before financing any chinese one belt one road projects they have dual use as military power projection enablers pattern neckties more are coming because i bought some cheap ones i don t think mickey will ever stop lying about his nonexistent achievements unfortunately some people believe him want a ticket to strangest things happen on new year eve like total strangers making out it is almost time for one more trip around the sun lack of data or even a conclusion won t stop some people from sticking to a false premise my phone has lately been ringing constantly and not from telemarketers it is time to find more bacon when the fed pushes the hyperinflation button most folks will have a lot less wealth
